The base coding agent runtime (agent.py, providers.py, tools.py, context.py,
config.py, compaction.py, memory.py, tool_registry.py) is forked from
nano-claude-code with optimizations for local small models.

Original contributions in this repository:
  - eval/evolve.py — DGM (Darwin Gödel Machine) self-evolution driver
  - eval/run_eval.py — eval harness with Circle Loop integration
  - eval/build_quixbugs_tasks.py — QuixBugs adapter
  - eval/smoke_test.py — pipeline sanity check
  - eval/tasks/task_01..task_13 — 13 hand-rolled bug-fix tasks
  - loop.py — Circle Loop iterative improvement engine

